columns.name: domain_name
columns.description: The name of the domain.

columns.name: arn
columns.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) specifying the domain.

columns.name: abuse_contact_email
columns.description: Email address to contact to report incorrect contact information for a domain,to report that the domain is being used to send spam, to report that someone is cyber squatting on a domain name, or report some other type of abuse.

columns.name: abuse_contact_phone
columns.description: Phone number for reporting abuse.

columns.name: admin_privacy
columns.description: Specifies whether contact information is concealed from WHOIS queries.

columns.name: auto_renew
columns.description: Indicates whether the domain is automatically renewed upon expiration.

columns.name: creation_date
columns.description: The date when the domain was created as found in the response to a WHOIS query.

columns.name: expiration_date
columns.description: The date when the registration for the domain is set to expire. The date and time is in Unix time format and Coordinated Universal time (UTC).

columns.name: registrant_privacy
columns.description: Specifies whether contact information is concealed from WHOIS queries.

columns.name: registrar_name
columns.description: Name of the registrar of the domain as identified in the registry. Domains with a .com, .net, or .org TLD are registered by Amazon Registrar.

columns.name: registrar_url
columns.description: Web address of the registrar.

columns.name: registry_domain_id
columns.description: Reserved for future use.

columns.name: reseller
columns.description: Reseller of the domain. Domains registered or transferred using Route 53 domains will have Amazon as the reseller.

columns.name: tech_privacy
columns.description: Specifies whether contact information is concealed from WHOIS queries.

columns.name: transfer_lock
columns.description: Indicates whether a domain is locked from unauthorized transfer to another party.

columns.name: updated_date
columns.description: The last updated date of the domain as found in the response to a WHOIS query.The date and time is in Unix time format and Coordinated Universal time (UTC).

columns.name: who_is_server
columns.description: The fully qualified name of the WHOIS server that can answer the WHOIS query for the domain.

columns.name: nameservers
columns.description: The name of the domain.

columns.name: registrant_contact
columns.description: Provides details about the domain registrant.

columns.name: status_list
columns.description: An array of domain name status codes, also known as Extensible Provisioning Protocol (EPP) status codes.

columns.name: tech_contact
columns.description: Provides details about the domain technical contact.

columns.name: admin_contact
columns.description: Provides details about the domain administrative contact.

columns.name: tags_src
columns.description: A list of tags assigned to the resource.
